These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, romance, sports, superhero
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, apricot, blue, orange, white
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance | disaster | superhero | sports |
| Color   | white    | blood-red | blue     | orange       | apricot  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, collecting, writing, puzzles
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Hobby   | collecting  | writing   | magic-tricks       | skydiving    | puzzles   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different games are played: billiard, domino, poker, chess, mah-jongg
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person playing domino is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Game        | poker | chess | domino | billiard | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

