.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, ice-hockey, surfing, snowboarding
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport   | surfing    | tennis        | ice-hockey | lacrosse | snowboarding |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

