.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, metal, blues, rock, electronic
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the fan of metal is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the fan of electronic is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock | blues | electronic | metal     |

