.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, handball, volleyball
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, chess, baking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | handball   | cricket   | baseball | volleyball | badminton |
| Hobby   | dancing | chess | baking   | singing | card-games       |

