.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, lilac, ivory, aquamarine, azure
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes lavender is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Color   | aquamarine | ivory | lilac | lavender   | azure |

