.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, cola, milk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | fanta       | milk | cola | hot-chocolate    |
| Sport   | tennis   | water-polo | soccer  | rugby     | ice-hockey |

