.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, marigold, iris, azalea
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | photography | camping | magic-tricks | woodworking | dancing |
| Flower   | marigold       | iris   | azalea         | zinnia   | orchid   |

