.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, italian, nigerian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, pall-mall, baccarat, bluemaster
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the british##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is the american##1
4. the italian is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian | argentine | british | american |
| Cigar           | bluemaster      | tiparillo    | baccarat  | bongani     | pall-mall     |

