.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: apple, artichoke, avocado, cherry, pomegranate
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, western, animation, spy, sports
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person eating cherry##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
