1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Flower    | poppy | daisy          | amaryllis    | balloon-flower | rose  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

