.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, coffee, water, fanta
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Beverage   | coffee | iced-tea      | water | tea | fanta |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

