5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | sprite | hot-chocolate | cola      | soy-milk | fanta      |
| Transport   | bike  | ship       | bus | quad-bike  | car |

