4. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Hobby   | dancing     | magic-tricks       | rock-climbing     | collecting  | puzzles  |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | cricket | tennis | handball |

